1. *Hitna* pomoć je došla brzo. (Emergency medical service came quickly.)
2. Molim vas da pozovete *hitnu* pomoć. (Please call the emergency medical service.)
3. Ovo je *hitna* situacija! (This is an emergency situation!)
4. Da li ste ikada bili u *hitnoj* situaciji? (Have you ever been in an emergency situation?)
5. *Hitnom* intervencijom su spasili život pacijenta. (They saved the patient's life with an emergency intervention.)
6. U bolnici je otvorena nova *hitna* služba. (A new emergency department has been opened at the hospital.)
7. *Hitni* sastanak je zakazan za sutra. (An emergency meeting has been scheduled for tomorrow.)
8. Država je poslala *hitnu* pomoć nakon prirodne katastrofe. (The government sent emergency aid after a natural disaster.)
9. Ukoliko imate *hitne* obaveze, odložite druženje za drugi put. (If you have urgent obligations, postpone the gathering for another time.)
10. *Hitnoj* situaciji se ne smete smejati. (You should not laugh at an emergency situation.)